      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion! It\u2019s in solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're heading to work or planning a fun weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go and drives like a dream. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it is!",
