      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example retains its factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing precise gear synchronization and tactile feedback. The chassis is structurally sound, having received documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent refresh of the trailing arm bushings. The VANOS unit has been professionally serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. While the finish displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power through the variable M differential lock. A driver-spec machine with a clean title, optimized for technical engagement.",
